tags.description: Carne Beach is at the southern extremity of this bay, St. Margaret's Beach about half a kilometer to the north and Ballytrent Beach about a kilometer north thereof.
Cullenstown beach is a southerly facing sandy beach located immediately west of where the River Muck enters the sea.
